# {{botany}} a [[botanical name]] at the rank of family. [[Circumscription]] and placement of the family will depend on [[taxonomic system]] or viewpoint. As accepted by the APG II system (2003) this family is smaller than in earlier literature and placed in the [[order]] ''[[Dipsacales]]'', which in turn is placed in the [[clade]] '''asterids'''.